e.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打pubg見到人都淆底射唔中啦<br />\n<br />\n真人駁火仲要冷靜到一槍射腳一槍射心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c488466e1ee6f41db15ad90356b97f7476606d","tid":608633,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3c053231daff22ecdff6483906a7481e2848805","tid":608633,"uid":92376,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180328/large/28ck4p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180328%2Flarge%2F28ck4p.jpg&h=f299f6f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d15b0d95d851f8470cd68a88f59e3f3f45b1eb","tid":608633,"uid":36857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:41:27.000Z","msg":"左膠真係社會癌細胞嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地準備開槍先（好彩卡彈，唔係警察都死撚埋），都仲話人執法過當<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲啲佢老母俾人用槍指住嗰陣，記得叫警察唔好執法過當<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18c81679cfaf7f1e016b5e8982c0585b1644d6d","tid":608633,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:15:08.000Z","msg":"台灣人 成日話自己治安好過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但台灣幾乎每隔 幾個星期就槍戰一次<br />\n<br />\n香港已經差唔多五年 無槍戰過, 對上一次已經係 2014年既啟晴邨槍擊案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}